                            <comment id="13909424" author="brocknoland" created="Sat, 22 Feb 2014 16:20:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I put a break fix into place for this but we should make the change and commit this so we don&apos;t regress.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=szehon&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;szehon&quot;&gt;szehon&lt;/a&gt; mentioned he was potentially interested in this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13921724" author="szehon" created="Thu, 6 Mar 2014 00:39:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Removed cp task from the batch-exec.vm template, also fixed the unit tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tested manually on my own cluster, and ran existing unit tests.  Let me know if more needs to be done.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13921814" author="brocknoland" created="Thu, 6 Mar 2014 01:12:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks great! &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can we also stop publishing the variables numOfFailedTests and maxSourceDirs to the template?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13921940" author="szehon" created="Thu, 6 Mar 2014 02:50:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure, no longer publishing those variables.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13921941" author="szehon" created="Thu, 6 Mar 2014 02:51:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adding link to RB&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13922678" author="brocknoland" created="Thu, 6 Mar 2014 16:01:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you Szehon! I have committed this to trunk!!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14210766" author="thejas" created="Thu, 13 Nov 2014 19:42:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has been fixed in 0.14 release. Please open new jira if you see any issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
